      "raw_text": "Work was begun this week by\nthe Washington Water Power COM\npany on the immense tunnel that\n10 to carry the waters Of the Spo-\nkane river underground from above\nthe falls to the region Of the Mon.\nroe street bridge.\n\n\nThis tunnel will be constructed\nfor the greater development Of\npower by means Of the falls. 1t is\none of the biggest undertakings in\nthe way OF power development ever\nundertaken in the northwest and\nwill cost millions before II is COM\npleted.\n\n\nThis Is the plan pursued In har-\nMessing the great Niagara on which\nwork has been in progress for\nyears."
